*《中国历代帝王传记丛书》<ref>{{cite news |title=中国历代帝王传记丛书 |url=https://book.douban.com/series/2220?page=1 |accessdate=2022-02-09 |archive-date=2022-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220424201316/https://book.douban.com/series/2220?page=1 }}</ref>

